'''伊万诺·迪奥尼吉''' ({{lang-it|Ivano Dionigi}}、[[佩萨罗|佩萨罗]]，1948年2月20日－)，意大利[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]学者，[[博洛尼亚大学|博洛尼亚大学]]现任校长(2009年至今)。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://video.gelocal.it/gazzettadimodena/dossier/festival-filosofia-2018-verita/lezioni-di-filosofia-in-pillole-ivano-dionigi-amore-e-verita-della-parola/102763/103369|title=Lezioni di filosofia in pillole. Ivano Dionigi: 'Amore e verità della parola'|date=2018-09-15|website=Video Gazzetta di Modena|language=en|access-date=2018-11-22|archive-date=2018-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122215615/https://video.gelocal.it/gazzettadimodena/dossier/festival-filosofia-2018-verita/lezioni-di-filosofia-in-pillole-ivano-dionigi-amore-e-verita-della-parola/102763/103369|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.baritoday.it/eventi/libro-possibile-winter-mazzariol-dionigi-bosco-bari-triggiano-gioia-colle-polignano-21-23-novembre-2018.html|title=Mazzariol, Dionigi e Bosco ospiti del Libro Possibile Winter|work=BariToday|access-date=2018-11-22|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216074557/https://www.baritoday.it/eventi/libro-possibile-winter-mazzariol-dionigi-bosco-bari-triggiano-gioia-colle-polignano-21-23-novembre-2018.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

迪奥尼吉在担任博洛尼亚大学校长前，为博洛尼亚大学拉丁文学教授。2012年11月10日，由教皇[[本篤十六世|本篤十六世]]任命为新成立的[[教皇拉丁学院|教皇拉丁学院]]主席<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/21/us-vatican-latin-idUSBRE8AK0UJ20121121|title=Vatican tweets on new Latin academy|accessdate=2014-05-23|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924172210/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/11/21/us-vatican-latin-idUSBRE8AK0UJ20121121|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

